<br>
IMO hardest parts are smithing and tailoring here.  At least star ruby steins are about 70pp per combine, sickle is about 300pp (failed 9 combines on sickle with 198 smithing +15% smithing item, ended up asking Inyx for help).  Tailoring is bad, because so few people have it at high levels.  Its only about 40pp per combine, so if yuo have 4k to waste, can just do 100 combines, most likely you'll make at least one (and get few skill ups while at that).<br>
<br>
Iron Oxides are pain to get, had to spent about 5 hours in the hole to get 2...and we were clearing quite a bit.<br>
<br>
Hrm any other random thoughts?  Yeah, no idea how hard is baking part, both times had to ask a friend for it.<br>
<br>
On the positive side I can make Demi-Secs realiably, so if you want one, send me a tell <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
